Weapon Types
============
These are the currently valid weapon types

    bludgeon        warrior and cleric classes
    magebludgeon    ALL
    slashing        warrior classes only
    thiefslashing   warrior and thief classes
    magicslashing   ALL - This is ONLY to be used for weapons created by spells.
    piercing        warrion classes only
    magepiercing    warrior, thief, and mage classes
    thiefpiercing   warrior and thief classes

warrior classes = fighter, cavalier, paladin, antipaladin, ranger, bard

